All Classes

Class Description
AutumnFactory
The AutumnFactory class is used to create objects in the autumn theme.
Coin
The coin class is used to create collectable coins for the player.
Collectable
The collectable class is the parent class of all collectables.
DesktopLauncher
Contains the main class of the game.
Enemy
The Enemy class is the parent class of all enemies.
Game
The Game class follows the singleton pattern, so there can only exist one instance of it.
Game.Season  
Hud
The hud of the game.
InteractiveObject
The InteravtiveObject class is the parent class of all object the player can interact with.
LevelEnd
The LevelEnd class is used to create an object at the end of the level for the player in order to finish it.
MainMenuScreen
Used to create the main menu screen of the game.
Player
The player class is used to create the player.
Player.State
The states of the player.
PlayScreen
The play screen which the user can see.
SeasonFactory
The SeasonFactory interface is used to create factories for every season.
SpringFactory
The SpringFactory class is used to create objects in the spring theme.
SummerFactory
The SummerFactory class is used to create objects in the summer theme.
Walker
The walker class is used to create walking enemies in a level.
WinterFactory
The WinterFactory class is used to create objects in the winter theme.
WorldContactListener
The WorldContactListener is used to create a contact listener for the game.
WorldCreator
Used to create all hitboxes and objects (Enemies, Collectables, LevelEnds) in a level.
